<style>
  .project {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .project-content {
    flex: 1;
    margin-right: 20px;
    margin-left: 20px;
    margin-top: 0;
    font-size: 20px;
  }

  .project-images {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .project-images img {
    max-width: calc(33.33% - 10px);
  }

  .button-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    font-size: 16px;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: 2px solid #007bff;
    color: #007bff;
    border-radius: 5px;
    font-weight: bold;
    }

</style>

<div class="button-container">
  <%= link_to "home", root_path, class: "btn" %>
  <%= link_to "about", about_path, class: "btn" %>
  <%= link_to "work", work_path, class: "btn" %>
  <%= link_to "contact", contact_path, class: "btn" %>
</div>

<main>

<div class="project">
  <div class="project-content">

    <h2>Project 1: Personal Website</h2>
    <h3>Description:</h3>
    <p>
      Designed my personal website to showcase my skills and projects in a more visually appealing and user-friendly manner.
    </p>

    <h3>Key Accomplishments:</h3>

    <p>
      Implemented a responsive design to ensure optimal viewing experience across devices.
      Integrated custom animations and transitions to enhance user engagement.
      Optimized website performance for faster load times and improved user experience.
    </p>

    <h3>Technologies Used:</h3>

    <p>
      HTML5
      CSS3 (Bootstrap)
      JavaScript (jQuery)
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="project-images">
  <img src="/assets/code.jpg" alt="Code">
  <img src="/assets/bootstrap.jpg" alt="Bootstrap">
  <img src="/assets/website.jpg" alt="Website">
</div>
</div>

<div class="project">
  <div class="project-content">

    <h2>Project 2: Chatbot for Customer Support</h2>

    <h3>Description:</h3>
    <p>
    Developed a chatbot to provide automated customer support for a web-based service. The chatbot assists users with common inquiries, provides relevant information, and guides them through troubleshooting steps.
    </p>

    <h3>Key Accomplishments:</h3>
    <p>
      Integrated the chatbot with the web-based service's backend system to access user data and provide personalized assistance.
      Designed conversational flows and scripted dialogues to engage users in interactive conversations and maintain a conversational tone.
      Enhanced the chatbot's capabilities over time through continuous learning and refinement based on user interactions and feedback.
    </p>

    <h3>Technologies Used:</h3>
    <p>
      HTML5
      CSS3 (Bootstrap)
      JavaScript (React.js)
      Node.js
      Socket.IO
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="project-images">
    <img src="/assets/chatbot.jpg" alt="Chatbot">
    <img src="/assets/nodejs.jpg" alt="Node.js">
    <img src="/assets/socket.jpg" alt="Socket">
  </div>
</div>
